{"tid":2319380,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實佩狗呢條友係咩問題？","createTime":"2020-12-10T05:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T15:40:37.000Z","uid":3204,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"caa9860fa093314fbefaab3b0a1f08e64beac802","tid":2319380,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得係佩狗先咁與別不同 <br />\n<br />\n其他人廢，好多時都係因為能力廢 <br />\n<br />\n但佩狗廢 <br />\n<br />\n好似同能力冇關 <br />\n<br />\n因為個人本身就廢 <br />\n<br />\n就算成個donald trump改名做佩電斯主席，感覺都係廢，一聽到個名果陣廢味就出晒黎 <br />\n<br />\n點解會咁？"},{"pid":"adb109e856f78182c456b16621f2bb1b8f406cec","tid":2319380,"uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:24:00.000Z","msg":"你廢過佩清囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佩清都會識掃雷，輯毒，跳火圈<br />\n你識都識？<br />\n<br />\n講消費，佩清食威莎，都係$10餐"},{"pid":"457e1e73428ffd1b606e82b65f58a0c8b98117ca","tid":2319380,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實樓主出左咩問題 係咁問人咩問題"},{"pid":"18a29d250eb5b566109b0922079e5cdc6c65a4a9","tid":2319380,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"457e1e73428ffd1b606e82b65f58a0c8b98117ca","tid":2319380,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實樓主出左咩問題 係咁問人咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"開po要問過你？"},{"pid":"b3633741ff241229a5e8426c2f4852a539e179c7","tid":2319380,"uid":3204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18a29d250eb5b566109b0922079e5cdc6c65a4a9","tid":2319380,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"457e1e73428ffd1b606e82b65f58a0c8b98117ca","tid":2319380,"uid":17606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實樓主出左咩問題 係咁問人咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"開po要問過你？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"秒左派狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/bi